                "institute": "4UKRKFT"
              },
              "free_text": [
                " Linear electron accelerator LU-40.",
                "Incident electron flux instability did not exceed 2%.",
                "A tantalum converter with a thickness of 1.05 mm was",
                "installed at the output of the electron accelerator;",
                "an aluminum electron moderator with a size of diameter",
                "90x100 mm was situated behind the converter. The",
                "distance from the Ta converter to the Al moderator was",
                "20 mm, and the distance to the studied sample was",
                "200 mm."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Samples of metallic zirconium in the form of a powder",
                "with a mass of 206.36 mg, enriched with the 90Zr",
                "isotope, and zirconium oxide with a mass of 463.9 mg,",
                "enriched with the 91Zr isotope, were used for",
                "irradiation."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "ACTIV"
              ],
              "free_text": [
